data.description: $1,000 AGENT BONUS!!!NEW ROOF WILL BE PUT ON BEFORE CLOSING!!! Nestled in a prestigious, tranquil neighborhood, this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers everything you need for comfortable family living. With an impressive oversized yard featuring a playground in the backyard, your family will have plenty of space to explore and play. Located within walking distance of the school, this prime location ensures convenience and a stress-free morning routine. Say goodbye to long commutes and hello to quality family time. Your children will benefit from the nearby school, creating a harmonious balance between education and home life. Step onto the inviting front porch and experience the charm and warmth of this home. The front porch serves as the perfect spot to relax, unwind, and connect with neighbors in this friendly community. In the backyard, spacious back porch provides an ideal setting for outdoor entertaining or enjoying a quiet evening with loved ones. Step inside and be greeted by the grandeur of vaulted ceilings, enhancing the feeling of space and openness. The well-designed layout seamlessly combines style and functionality, creating an inviting atmosphere for everyday living. The convenience of an indoor laundry room adds to the comfort and practicality of this home. Enjoy the ease of having everything you need right at your fingertips. Priced to sell, this fantastic home presents an incredible opportunity for you and your family. With its family-friendly neighborhood, luscious yard, and proximity to amenities, it is the perfect place to create lasting memories. Don't wait! This ideal family home in a sought-after location won't stay on the market for long. Call now to schedule your visit and discover the potential that awaits you and your loved ones. All information taken from the tax record, and while deemed reliable, cannot be guaranteed.
